<%- include('../includes/head.ejs') %>

<head>
    <!-- Google Font -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f7fc; /* Light background color */
            color: #333; /* Dark text for better readability */
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .main-content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .page-title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #333; /* Dark color for title */
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px; /* Spacing below the title */
        }

        .content {
            background-color: black; /* White background for the content section */
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px; /* Rounded corners */
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* Soft shadow for depth */
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto; /* Center content horizontally */
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem; /* Heading size for subsections */
            color: #007bff; /* Blue color for subsections */
            margin-bottom: 10px; /* Spacing below the heading */
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.6; /* Increased line height for readability */
            margin-bottom: 20px; /* Spacing below paragraphs */
        }

        a {
            color: #007bff; /* Blue color for links */
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s; /* Smooth transition on hover */
        }

        a:hover {
            color: #0056b3; /* Darker blue on hover */
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #333; /* Dark background for the footer */
            color: #fff; /* White text for contrast */
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            position: fixed; /* Fixed at the bottom of the page */
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            z-index: 1000; /* Ensure footer stays on top */
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
<%- include('../includes/navigation.ejs') %>

<div class="main-content" id="mainContent">
    <main>
        <div class="content">
            <h1 class="page-title">Privacy Policy</h1>

            <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
            <p>Welcome to the Lost and Found Portal. As a student project designed to help my friends and college mates, this platform allows users to upload and view images of lost or found items. Your privacy is important to us, and this privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your information.</p>

            <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>We collect the following information when you use our platform:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, contact number, email (optional), and item details.</li>
                <li><strong>Images:</strong> Photos of the lost/found items you upload.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>3. Use of Information</h2>
            <p>The collected information is used for the following purposes:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>To display uploaded items on the platform for others to view.</li>
                <li>To contact you regarding the items you upload or inquire about.</li>
                <li>To enhance the user experience and troubleshoot any issues.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>4. Data Protection</h2>
            <p>We take reasonable precautions to protect your personal data. However, as this is a student project, we do not guarantee absolute security, and you are using the platform at your own risk.</p>

            <h2>6. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please feel free to <a href="mailto:example@example.com">contact us</a>.</p>

            <div class="footer">
                &copy; 2025 Lost and Found Portal. All Rights Reserved.
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</div>

</body>
</html>
